title: Brad Paisley Stops By + Bobby Gets Trashed Online For Making It To Dancing With The Stars Finals

description:
Brad Paisley stops by to World Premiere his new single "Bucked Off." Bobby gets trashed online for making it through to the DWTS Finals. Also, Keith Urban tells Amy the full story about the lady who paid for his meal a few weeks ago.
